sg":"自pish 4/10"},{"pid":"0cdd2976deedee11490bc591d736ce8660cfc73e","tid":1543520,"uid":226421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T08:14:55.000Z","msg":"自pish 5/10"},{"pid":"37e76e60886aaf8cec8b4c44d59eca538a095c97","tid":1543520,"uid":249705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T08:14:58.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">下星期一 9月9 大專罷課集會</span></span><br />\n<br />\n作為大專生<br />\n今次開學罷課搞到咁柒<br />\n完全俾中學生比下去<br />\n知道大家好慚愧 好想付出更多<br />\n<br />\n短時間內嘅主題<br />\n係要美國國會通過香港人權法案<br />\n既然7號有塞機場 8號有美國領事館<br />\n點解我哋大專生<br />\n唔襯中學生9號一週一罷<br />\n一齊搞多次罷課集會<br />\n有聲勢浩大既民意表態<br />\n既可以團聚學界<br />\n又為之後嘅三罷打強心針<br />\n<br />\n7號8號9號 一連三日嘅大型示威集會<br />\n就可以show到民意支持<br />\n俾美國國會順利表決通過條人權法<br />\n<br />\n香港就快死啦<br />\n一齊撐住好唔好<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><br />\n洗版洗到有組織搞9月9罷課為止</span></span>"},{"pid":"d92160807eb5eb88e87984194c264a63dd0ae444","tid":1543520,"uid":226421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T08:15:06.000Z","msg":"自pish 6/10"},{"pid":"1e3b0826585f3903cf35c787751242c944c905ef","tid":1543520,"uid":226421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T08:15:17.000Z","msg":"自pish 7/10"},{"pid":"b2f8d7a391bbcd6785babf7d95adc336b7e36fef","tid":1543520,"uid":226421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T08:15:27.000Z","msg":"自pish 8/10"},{"pid":"9b549f9900a4c32458a92e7d01fae5de7b094750","tid":1543520,"uid":226421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T08:15:38.000Z","msg":"自pish 9/10"},{"pid":"c465a5e3f1c5ea88316953e953ddd8fff9dd4e45","tid":1543520,"uid":226421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T08:15:48.000Z","msg":"自pish 10/10"},{"pid":"1de472d21cc2307480093ef830ad52dde37a104c","tid":1543520,"uid":5523,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T08:16:11.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: maroon;\">主<br />\n權<br />\n在<br />\n民</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">香<br />\n港<br />\n獨<br />\n立</span></span>"},{"pid":"7239126fa164b2bf34d284e6b6819b00116de973","tid":1543520,"uid":226421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T08:16:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=zdS50W9Aq_Y\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DzdS50W9Aq_Y&d=g6cJT0UyhZ9RanxftZ%2B8MKCH8iT5eEApQhURqQe1KTk%3D&h=d228d94e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=zdS50W9Aq_Y</a>"},{"pid":"8ef22314d554c63f242b1ee2d8b9064ec8397ee4","tid":1543520,"uid":51790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T08:17:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcbf461366df5804c5c5eb2c36868a1f9285781e","tid":1543520,"uid":302831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T08:17:58.000Z","msg":"一齊打經濟戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n抵制藍色餐廳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com/maps/d/viewer?mid=10SCYSkgC9KMC_kAGtLChlGRLWVbk8NTs&amp;shorturl=1&amp;ll=22.289809900000016%2C114.1965917&amp;z=17\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Fmaps%2Fd%2Fviewer%3Fmid%3D10SCYSkgC9KMC_kAGtLChlGRLWVbk8NTs%26shorturl%3D1%26ll%3D22.289809900000016%252C114.1965917%26z%3D17&d=g6cJT0UyhZ9RanxftZ%2B8MKCH8iT5eEApQhURqQe1KTk%3D&h=b0b09d82\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com/maps/d/viewer?mid=10SCYSkgC9KMC_kAGtLChlGRLWVbk8NTs&amp;shorturl=1&amp;ll=22.289809900000016%2C114.1965917&amp;z=17</a>"},{"pid":"f3226ab7869bf239a9953a1249a6732e68572982","tid":1543520,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T08:18:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a86e4bd84e279e5b9600cbd09248c0dbac5a1295","tid":1543520,"uid":226421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T08:19:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/2902258\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F2902258&d=g6cJT0UyhZ9RanxftZ%2B8MKCH8iT5eEApQhURqQe1KTk%3D&h=6aee6e02\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F2902258&h=d6d44c63\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/2902258</a><br />\n美擬向中國討清朝1兆美元債券 他曝：針對這弱點攻擊<br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕美國與中國貿易戰持續延燒，有外媒報導，美國將向中國追討清朝高達1兆美元的債券。對此，醫師、作家蔡依橙表示，美國這招是有趣的一招，因為要求中國處理清朝債券，就是<span style=\"color: red;\">針對「中華論述」的弱點攻擊</span>。<br />\n<br />\n清朝政府1911年為了資助湖廣鐵路建設而出售了這批債券，這批國債即為「湖廣鐵路五厘利息遞還金英鎊借款債券（湖廣債）」。（擷取自ebay拍賣網）<br />\n清朝政府1911年為了資助湖廣鐵路建設而出售了這批債券，這批國債即為「湖廣鐵路五厘利息遞還金英鎊借款債券（湖廣債）」。（擷取自ebay拍賣網）<br />\n<br />\n《彭博商業周刊》報導，清朝政府在1911年為了資助湖廣鐵路建設而出售這批債券，這批國債即為「湖廣鐵路五厘利息遞還金英鎊借款債券（湖廣債）」，但清朝被推翻後，中華民國一直不承認這些債券，1949年，中共也同樣不認，不過美國人數十年來都持續追討這筆債務。<br />\n<br />\n對此，蔡依橙在臉書粉專「蔡依橙的閱讀筆記」發文指出，來幫大家科普一下，美國這招為什麼是有趣的招，因為要求中國處理清國債券，就是針對「中華論述」的弱點攻擊。因為中華民國跟中華人民共和國，在面對清國遺產的時候，都是「只要權利、不要義務」的無賴作法，這當然是不行的。<br />\n<br />\n蔡依橙說，實務上，就是清國領土都說是他們的，都是固有領土；但清國債務跟條約這些固有義務都不認。這在國際法上當然是無賴。「以前中國弱，大家幫你忙，不跟你計較，先幫你富起來，慢慢進入國際社會。現在你覺得自己強了，中國製造2025，在太平洋上要跟美國對分（習近平言：太平洋容得下兩個國家），那我們就來平等相待吧，先從債務開始算起」。<br />\n<br />\n蔡依橙指出，中共當然是不想認的，但中國不認這個債務，那就別說自己是中國道統，也別說跟清國有繼承關係，別再鬼扯固有領土。「這個很嚴重，因為一旦中華人民共和國與清國權利義務脫勾，那中國就沒有道理宣稱香港是他的、台灣是他的、新疆是他的、西藏是他的、東北是他的。」<br />\n<br />\n蔡依橙強調，為什麼香港也扯進來呢？因為<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">事實上割讓香港的南京條約正本在故宮，真要照國際法走，中共根本沒理由控制香港</span></span>。「<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">這招，就是在讓全世界認清，中共是個不講道理、不講法律、不講權利義務，只會鬼扯的政權。離一個負責任的世界大國，還非常遙遠。</span></span>」"},{"pid":"43d3139511c416e2b131e472a7b91cd3c0afd599","tid":1543520,"uid":226421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T08:20:47.000Z","msg":"歸還清債，落實主權<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a72732b868853c9b3f05dc03d24fcb4189c5891","tid":1543520,"uid":45400,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T08:20:52.000Z","msg":"［緊急］林鄭已交出輿論戰核彈！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1540998\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1540998</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"5bc8194a680cd207d6c93dbf0ed3074a378e437c","tid":1543520,"uid":35790,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T08:22:18.000Z","msg":"港人自救   主權在民"},{"pid":"46417cb56d915cb42a7e91ad57ab1d3c3512d93a","tid":1543520,"uid":181035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T08:23:21.000Z","msg":"歸還清債，落實主權<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36c39f96c2c3b5c64ae4939ac4ced5666e7ccfd9","tid":1543520,"uid":226421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T08:23:32.000Z","msg":"歸還清債 落實主權<br />\n港人自救 主權在民"},{"pid":"a47e1504c512c0bb77016b9e603c676611bb26bc","tid":1543520,"uid":67553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T08:24:17.000Z","msg":"落實主權即係咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />釐清定檢視定點？"},{"pid":"7f73d8af744ac8e174f58fc5ad00d03e58b8727b","tid":1543520,"uid":67553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5bc8194a680cd207d6c93dbf0ed3074a378e437c","tid":1543520,"uid":35790,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T08:22:18.000Z","msg":"港人自救   主權在民"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T08:24:36.000Z","msg":"港人自治 主權在民"},{"pid":"c662787da80e89455dbbdd9ce9a5fee9bc3ae79a","tid":1543520,"uid":273991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T08:25:28.000Z","msg":"還錢"},{"pid":