uid":67553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"20c3e4c27f330a02864e498d3a7dfe464b30d55d","tid":1543520,"uid":226421,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a47e1504c512c0bb77016b9e603c676611bb26bc","tid":1543520,"uid":67553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T08:24:17.000Z","msg":"落實主權即係咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />釐清定檢視定點？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T08:29:17.000Z","msg":"對於香港既主權，你唔認數，你拎香港做咩？加上所謂「不平等」條約正本係放係台灣"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T08:40:12.000Z","msg":"咁唔用&ldquo;落實&rdquo; 好似好啲喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T08:44:39.000Z","msg":"以證主權？"},{"pid":"da90be783ba32c9cd1894d724657700efd26a452","tid":1543520,"uid":226421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T08:49:21.000Z","msg":"歸還清債 以證主權"},{"pid":"f09469638e7d3c7703f58bf60c9f27e03bbc90eb","tid":1543520,"uid":72800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T08:51:04.000Z","msg":"還債！還普選！<br />\n還義士！還眼！還自由俾香港人呀！！！！<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><blockquote><em>我們成長為自由人。 沒人可讓一個自由的人下跪。<br />\nWe grew up as free people. No one can make a free person kneel.</em><br />\n<span style=\"color: navy;\"><strong><del>WINTER ON FIRE</del><br />\n《HONG KONG BE WATER》</strong></span></blockquote></div><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">港共殺人政權企圖以<strong>錄音、撤回、學季開始</strong><br />\n轉移<strong>太子地鐵傷亡、<br />\n六警壓脊椎休克 <span style=\"color: teal;\">至今嚴重昏迷</span>、<br />\n新屋嶺事件、<span style=\"color: violet;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">阻止民主人權法案</span></strong></span>、<br />\n模糊 臥底實彈、武警滲透、<span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">清朝債主權問題</span></span>等<br />\n[/size=5]</strong>[/red]連串<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>核彈</strong></span>事件焦點<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">林鄭錄音：事件現時已經上升至「國家主權及國家安全的層次，\n加上世界兩大經濟體前所未有的張力」，她可以做的已經非常少。</code></pre><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: right;\"><blockquote><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">英、美、德 領事館請願 大遊行</span></span></strong><br />\n國際審視中英聯合聲明 法定性<br />\n中共正統性<br />\n中共毀約 無視國際社會<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />請求國際介入香港前途</span></span></strong> <br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">施壓制裁港府 <br />\n還原港人高度自治 落實港人雙普選 <br />\n協助<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">重新制定</span>民主進程<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></strong><br />\n香港人道災難 <strong>高壓滅聲</strong> 白色恐怖 <br />\n執法機器無法無天 受命中共 <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: brown;\">港府管治班子自治權名存實亡</span>  聽命中央</span><br />\n實彈恐嚇 威嚇扼殺<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">民主自由</span>現代普世價值<br />\n<br />\n重申 <strong><ins>五大政諫<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />全面落實</ins></strong><br />\n<strong><em><span style=\"color: green;\">驅逐共黨 光復香港<br />\n華夏遺珠 高度自治</span> </em></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: violet;\">人權民主法案</span> 事在必行</strong></blockquote></div><br />\n<br />\n[center]<strong>這不單是 反修例活動<br />\n這是屬於香港人的<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">時代革命</span></strong></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><ins>流水革命 元年</ins></span></strong></div>"},{"pid":"df6a12d5410ed7c0832b40377e05a82037a7e45c","tid":1543520,"uid":280044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T08:51:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"912350b3251818fd3e9a2e887a45a20c0e1f8895","tid":1543520,"uid":226421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f09469638e7d3c7703f58bf60c9f27e03bbc90eb","tid":1543520,"uid":72800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T08:51:04.000Z","msg":"還債！還普選！<br /